README for my bin dir

Contains some scripts for my use 
feel free to have fun with them ;)

###
vga

requires: xrandr, perl

perl script to turn on VGA1 on my thinkpad
	$>vga [left|right|clone|off]

###
mute

requires: alsamixer, perl

mutes the speaker on my thinkpad, NOT the Master

	$>mute 						#toggles on and off, when no @ARGV is given
	$>mute [on|off|status|?]	

